{"id": "1512789064632373349", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "沙耶の隣を今ファイントサルバドルまで固定にしててあと一人を悩んでます。\nタイスを最初は取りに行こうかと思ってたんですけどファイントと組むなら実はワンダかナウティラで反撃に寄せた方がいいのか？とか考えたんですけど自信がないのでアドバイス欲しいです。", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:03:39.270000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512790221635457146", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "975004866479026256", "author_name": "0w04250", "author_bot": false, "content": "ワンダ良きと思われます👍", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:08:15.121000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512790391575806114", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドルの凸が進んで無かったり餅札が無かったりすると、アタッカーいないから火力出せるキャラ入れた方が楽かも\nサルバドルで現状火力足りてるならサルバドルの２コスを使い回せる編成の方が良い", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:08:55.638000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512790496022630441", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドル2凸です！", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:09:20.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512790691879714847", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "所持してるアタッカーがヘロットなんですけどサルバドルと合わせると全体的に重い感じがして上手く扱えませんでした……", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:10:07.236000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512790879738269798", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "２凸でダメージ足りてます？\n３凸のこれで結構火力上がるんですよね\nあとモチーフ札", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:10:52.025000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1512790879339937892", "filename": "Screenshot_20260606-211001.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1767278, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1512790879339937892/Screenshot_20260606-211001.png?ex=6a33e04b&is=6a328ecb&hm=c1cea4f5e68a043d1aa9c2d96d2812947f163f5b564c40847143ad010403f5de&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512791105756991518", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "まだあんまり難しいとこまで行ってないので今は足りてます。", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:11:45.912000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512791227077099601", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "ただヘロット入れた方が火力は出てるなぁとは思います", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:12:14.837000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512791604245823539", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "火力で困ってるので無ければ持ってればワンダとかでも良いと思います！\nあとは恒常だとカーシアとかかな？\n基本的に他の界域と混ぜた方が強いので！", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:13:44.761000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
