{"id": "1512792288546390047", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "ならワンダとかで試してみるのも良いかもですね(持ってるなら)\n超次元空間が強いのでサルバドルの２コスを放り込んでおけば大抵何とかなります", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:16:27.911000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512792568302407690", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "412941973884895232", "author_name": "shibu0097", "author_bot": false, "content": "ワンダは所持だけしてます。\nナウティラ1凸と迷ってたんですけど効果だけ見ればワンダ強そうだなーと思って聞いてみました", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T12:17:34.610000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
