{"id": "1512644893351219280", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1169816536882626594", "author_name": "tenseikarennatomato_82997", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:30:46.158000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1512644891791069255", "filename": "IMG_4320.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1095845, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1512644891791069255/IMG_4320.png?ex=6a340115&is=6a32af95&hm=e15eba9a3dfec387d547e6efd90b9c15e7c609b93fa8f33aae1e776d928d3579&"}, {"id": "1512644892218626118", "filename": "IMG_4321.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1055650, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1512644892218626118/IMG_4321.png?ex=6a340115&is=6a32af95&hm=b4ac2f62b48fe9d98b444546219a87ddbaf38f8d2bb7b97a327f7487443a87f0&"}, {"id": "1512644892671873054", "filename": "IMG_4322.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1098579, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1512644892671873054/IMG_4322.png?ex=6a340115&is=6a32af95&hm=4b6ed288190096afece32942cba491570f053543ba7e61bc638c4de3252a8199&"}, {"id": "1512644893086974053", "filename": "IMG_4323.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1086423, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1512644893086974053/IMG_4323.png?ex=6a340116&is=6a32af96&hm=7c8f7e4bf5b8fd45077d11278586c92a405e28087d45b4e17db60097ce53d559&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512646455213555783", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "自分は血ヘロ使っている時は血ヘロアイギスサルバタイスで組んでいます。手持ちならこの4人でも大丈夫だと思います。", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:36:58.535000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512648030535549238", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "血ヘロは\n・1コスで自身に血鎖状態を付ける\n・血鎖は、被ダメ上昇&被ダメで\"殺意\"を獲得、殺意の上限100\n・殺意は狂気解放で除去し、解放を打ったターンの「攻撃」の最終効果が殺意1点ごとに2.0%上昇\n・1コスを3回使った後に変化する4コスで対象の出血即時発動&出血2倍ダメージ\nって感じなので、道中で殺意を貯めて、最終戦では、狂気解放→2コス使用→4コス使用で一発デカいダメージを出す感じです", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:43:14.121000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:44:12.703000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512648249276891207", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1169816536882626594", "author_name": "tenseikarennatomato_82997", "author_bot": false, "content": "ということは、行動力6は欲しいってことですかね", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:44:06.273000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512648336610562078", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1169816536882626594", "author_name": "tenseikarennatomato_82997", "author_bot": false, "content": "策謀とか、注射器遺物とか", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:44:27.095000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1512648447268749484", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "そうですね、出来れば欲しいかなとは思うんですけど、沙耶餅で行動力上限が増やせるのと", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T02:44:53.478000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
